description: The state-run IRNA media outlet reported that the aircraft carrying Raisi and other senior officials went down as the president returned from an event on the border with Azerbaijan.
title: A helicopter carrying Iranian President Ebrahim Raisi went down in a 'hard landing'

description: There's trouble in the town of Bad Göodsburg! A wishing well has stopped working! NPR's Tamara Keith talks with Jess Hannigan about her new children's book, "Spider in the Well."
title: Hold on to your wishes — there's a 'Spider in the Well'
